👉 Custom-VPC

If you don’t select VPC, it won’t allow you to continue.

✅ 3️⃣ Connectivity Type

You must select:

✔ Public

Do NOT choose Private.

Why?

Because:

NAT Gateway must sit in a public subnet

It needs Internet Gateway access

So leave Public selected.

✅ 4️⃣ Elastic IP Allocation

